	"system": {
		"description": "<p>Heartberry is found in fern gullies and on mountain slopes. The spear-shaped leaves have toothed edges, and stalks bear either a single white flower or a dark berry. The berries are used to neutralize poisons and prevent infections.</p>\n<p><em><strong>Effect.</strong></em> When you consume the berries, you are granted an expertise die on saving throws vs poison and disease for the next 24-hours.</p>",
